## Color Conventions

### Brand Colors (to be defined)
- Primary: `blue-600` for main actions
- Secondary: `gray-600` for secondary actions
- Success: `green-600` for positive actions
- Warning: `yellow-600` for warnings
- Danger: `red-600` for destructive actions

### Text Colors
- Primary text: `text-gray-900`
- Secondary text: `text-gray-600`
- Muted text: `text-gray-500`
- Light text on dark: `text-white`

### Background Colors
- Page background: `bg-gray-50` or `bg-white`
- Card background: `bg-white`
- Hover states: `hover:bg-gray-100`

## Spacing Conventions

### Consistent Spacing Scale
- `space-y-2` - Tight vertical spacing (0.5rem)
- `space-y-4` - Normal vertical spacing (1rem)
- `space-y-6` - Loose vertical spacing (1.5rem)
- `space-y-8` - Extra loose spacing (2rem)

### Padding and Margins
- Components: `p-4` or `p-6` for consistent internal spacing
- Sections: `py-8` or `py-12` for vertical section spacing
- Container: `px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8` for responsive horizontal padding

